WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:08.660 --> 00:00:09.980
NIGHT NIGHT

00:00:09.980 --> 00:00:12.000
(EVERYONE) NIGHT NIGHT ROSIE

00:00:12.700 --> 00:00:17.460
(DISTANT ROAR)

00:00:17.460 --> 00:00:20.655
(GIGGLE) PARDON YOU RAGGLES

00:00:20.655 --> 00:00:21.980
IT WASN'T ME

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:24.974
WELL IF IT WASN'T RAGGLES

00:00:24.974 --> 00:00:26.317
WHERE DID IT COME FROM?

00:00:26.740 --> 00:00:29.040
(DISTANT ROAR)

00:00:29.040 --> 00:00:32.960
OH, THAT NOISE IS FUNNY

00:00:33.240 --> 00:00:35.480
I WONDER WHAT'S MAKING IT

00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:40.160
THE N- N- N- NOISE, CAN'T SAY I NOTICED

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:44.180
MAYBE ROSIE WILL KNOW WHERE THE NOISE IS COMING FROM

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:46.280
OHHH

00:00:47.620 --> 00:00:51.120
(DISTANT ROAR AND THEN DOOR BELL)

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:52.580
WHAT WAS THAT?

00:00:52.580 --> 00:00:54.400
THERE'S SOMEBODY AT THE DOOR

00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:55.468
COME ON ROSIE

00:00:55.468 --> 00:00:57.788
LET'S GO AND SEE WHO IT IS

00:01:01.880 --> 00:01:03.140
WHO IS IT?

00:01:03.140 --> 00:01:04.800
IT'S ONLY US

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:07.760
HELLO BLUEBIRD, BIG BEAR

00:01:07.760 --> 00:01:10.300
DID YOU HEAR THE NOISE TOO?

00:01:11.060 --> 00:01:13.120
YES, FUNNY ISN'T IT?

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:17.260
I COULDN'T HEAR ANYTHING

00:01:17.260 --> 00:01:18.600
(DISTANT ROAR)

00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:22.520
OHHHH! THAT NOISE!

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:25.320
I WONDER WHAT'S MAKING IT

00:01:25.320 --> 00:01:26.180
I DON'T KNOW

00:01:26.974 --> 00:01:28.974
LET'S FIND OUT 

00:01:30.860 --> 00:01:33.680
MAYBE IT'S A MONSTER 

00:01:34.638 --> 00:01:36.198
WITH THREE HEADS

00:01:36.300 --> 00:01:38.920
AND 16 LEGS

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:42.920
WITH PURPLE AND YELLOW HAIR

00:01:43.060 --> 00:01:46.180
LALALALALALA

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:49.040
(GIGGLE) IT'S OKAY BLUEBIRD

00:01:49.620 --> 00:01:51.620
THEY'RE ONLY PRETENDING 

00:01:51.754 --> 00:01:53.494
YOU DON'T NEED TO BE SCARED

00:01:53.500 --> 00:02:01.220
SCARED? (LAUGHING) OH NO, EVEN IF THERE'S A MONSTER I COULD MAGIC IT AWAY

00:02:01.220 --> 00:02:02.520
IF I WANTED TO 

00:02:02.600 --> 00:02:06.700
I'M JUST HERE T- T- T- TO CHECK YOU'RE ALL OKAY

00:02:08.060 --> 00:02:11.100
(DISTANT ROAR) AHHHHH!

00:02:11.240 --> 00:02:14.680
I'M FINE, ABSOLUTELY FINE

00:02:15.200 --> 00:02:16.820
THERE THERE BIG BEAR

00:02:16.826 --> 00:02:17.820
IT'S OKAY

00:02:17.820 --> 00:02:19.530
REALLY

00:02:19.530 --> 00:02:20.416
IT IS 

00:02:21.840 --> 00:02:25.320
A NOISE IS DEFINITELY COMING FROM OUTSIDE

00:02:25.700 --> 00:02:28.920
I THINK I HAVE HEARD A NOISE LIKE THIS BEFORE

00:02:29.720 --> 00:02:33.236
MAYBE IN A THUNDER STORM

00:02:33.236 --> 00:02:35.396
IT DOESN'T LOOK STORMY

00:02:35.773 --> 00:02:38.093
THERE AREN'T ANY CLOUDS

00:02:38.100 --> 00:02:39.780
OR RAIN

00:02:40.135 --> 00:02:42.135
OH, I LOVE STORMS

00:02:42.140 --> 00:02:43.820
THE LOUDER, THE BETTER

00:02:43.820 --> 00:02:47.140
I DON'T, STORMS CAN BE SCARY 

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:50.580
OH, I'M NOT SCARED OF STORMS

00:02:50.860 --> 00:02:53.300
I'M NOT SCARED OF ANYTHING 

00:02:53.300 --> 00:02:55.080
(DISTANT ROAR) WAHHHH!

